name: tezos-artcast stamp remix for gratitude #1
description: The tezos-artcast stamp was originally created by @flygohr exclusively for the tezos-artcast. Artist pc84(@pc8417) remixed the logo with #noisedeck. Now we at the tezos-artcast are giving out these tokens to the beating heart of the project: artists who we have shared on the tezos-artcast.xyz
